snippet.title: Captain Sabertooth and the Magic Diamond Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the first trailer for Captain Sabertooth and the Magic Diamond, an epic pirate adventure for the whole family!🏴‍☠️ Set sails to adventure this holiday season 🦜⚓

Learn more about the game on our website:
http://playcaptainsabertooth.com/
